title: Troy Ave White Christmas 2  mixtape
description:
Troy Ave is back at it this Holiday Season with part 2 of of his now annual "White Christmas" mixtape series. Last year hosted by DJ Holiday, this year Troy Ave taps DJ Drama host and present Part 2. Features include 2 Chainz, Uncle Murda, Lloyd Banks & more as well as produtcion from Yankee, Chase N Cashe and Statik Selektah among others. Follow on twitter @TroyAveBSB


1.Merry White Christmas (Prod by Yankee) 
2.Lost Boyz ft. 2 Chainz (Prod by Ziggy Beats) 
3.Brooklyn Shit ft. Uncle Murda (Prod by IllaTracks) 
4.Fuk You Pay Me ft. Avon Blocksdale (Prod by Yankee) 
5.Go Getter (Prod by Teamwork Music) 
6.Greetings & Salutations 
7.Do It ft. Styles P (Prod by Mike Reazon) 
8.Your Style ft. Lloyd Banks (Prod by Chase N Cashe) 
9.Glitter and Gold (Prod by Statik Selektah) 
10.Roll With It ft. King Sevin (Prod by Chase N Cashe) 
11.If You Got It Like That ft. Young Lito (Prod by Chase N Cashe) 
12.Do Better (Prod by John Scino) 
13.My Lifetime
